This is a console-based version of the Blackjack card game.

Simple Idea :
    Player(P) plays against a Dealer controlled by PC
    Features :
        - Simple text-based BlackJack game
        - One player versus an automated dealer.
        - The player can stand or hit.
        - Player will be able to pick their betting amount.
        - Player is able to keep track of his\her total Coins.
        - Alert the player of wins, losses, or busts, etc...